# Summary
The Experiment Evaluation API documentation describes two key endpoints: the Evaluation API (/v1/vardata) for retrieving variant assignments for users through remote evaluation, and the Flags API (/v1/flags) for downloading flag configurations for local evaluations, both requiring deployment key authentication.

